snippet.title: Trans-Galactic Tournament - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Choose your champions and prepare for wild interstellar combat that's easy to learn yet challenging to master!

http://www.playtgt.com

Welcome to Trans-Galactic Tournament!  TGT is a hilarious action-packed MOBA, designed and optimized for the PlayStation 4 and completely Free-to-Play.  Compete with or against your friends in intense 4v4 online matches in 3 incredibly fun and unique multiplayer modes spanning the entire galaxy, in stunningly lethal locations.  Collect and customize outrageous champions, each with powerfully unique abilities, weapons and styles of play.

© KizStudios Inc. All rights reserved.
